item.title: AI Expert Talks No-Code Computer Vision on Startuprad.io
item.description: Executive Summary In this episode of Startuprad.io, we delve into the world of AI and computer vision with our guest Simone Trevisan, a computer vision expert and project manager at Blue Tensor. Simone shares insights into the innovative computer vision platform, Iris, designed for small and medium-sized industries to harness AI without the need for coding expertise. He also discusses Blue Tensor's collaboration with Huawei to deploy their platform on both on-premise and cloud servers... Feed: https://deeptechgermany.podcaster.de/deeptechgermany.rss
